search_results.title: Paul McKenna
search_results.snippet: Paul McKenna (born 8 November 1963) is a British hypnotist, behavioural scientist, television and radio broadcaster and author of self-help books.

search_results.title: About Paul
search_results.snippet: Paul McKenna, PhD. Is an international best-selling author. His books have sold more than ten million copies and have been translated into 32 languages.

search_results.title: Paul McKenna – Keynote Speaker
search_results.snippet: Paul McKenna is an international best-selling author whose books have sold more than seven million copies and been translated into 32 languages.
